<p><strong>Starter (Leaven)</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>75 g all-purpose flour</li>
  <li>50 g starter</li>
  <li>50 g filtered water</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Dough</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>300 g all-purpose flour</li>
  <li>150 g water</li>
  <li>100 g bubbly starter</li>
</ul>

